<div id="infobox" class="infobox"> 
 <div class="table-responsive"> 
  <table class="wiki_table"> 
   <tbody> 
    <tr> 
     <th style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"> <h2>Comet Azur</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img style="width: 200px; height: 200px;" title="Comet Azur" src="/file/Elden-Ring/comet_azur_sorcery_elden_ring_wiki_guide_200px.png" alt="comet azur sorcery elden ring wiki guide 200px" width="200" height="200"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>Spell Type</td> 
     <td><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Primeval Sorceries" href="/Primeval+Sorceries" target="">Primeval Sorceries</a></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td>FP Cost 40 (10)</td> 
     <td>Slots Used 3</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td colspan="2"><img title="item_effect_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_18px" src="/file/Elden-Ring/item_effects_icon_elden_ring_wiki_guide_55px_18px.png" alt="item effects icon elden ring wiki guide 55px 18px" width="18" height="18">Effect 
      <div class="lineleft">
        Fires a tremendous comet within a starry torrent 
      </div> <br><img style="float: left;" title="Attributes Requirement" src="/file/Elden-Ring/attributes-required-elden-ring-wiki-guide-18.png" alt="attributes required elden ring wiki guide 18" width="18" height="18">Requires 
      <div class="lineleft"> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Intelligence" href="/Intelligence" target="">Intelligence</a> 60 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Faith" href="/Faith" target="">Faith</a>&nbsp;0 
       <br> 
       <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Arcane" href="/Arcane" target="">Arcane</a>&nbsp;0 
      </div> </td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p><strong>Comet Azur</strong> is a&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Sorceries" href="/Sorceries" target="">Sorcery</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Comet Azur spell</strong> creates a giant comet that deals very high damage from a great distance.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>Legendary sorcery devised by Azur, primeval sorcerer.<br></em></p> 
 <p><em>Fires a tremendous comet in a torrent akin to the distant starry expanse, the place said to be the origin of glintstone.<br>Hold to continue releasing the sorcery's power.<br></em></p> 
 <p><em>When Azur glimpsed into the primeval current, he saw darkness. He was left both bewitched and fearful of the abyss.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Comet Azur</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Comet Azur</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li> <p><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Hermit Village" href="/Hermit+Village" target="">Hermit Village</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Mt Gelmir" href="/Mt+Gelmir">Mt. Gelmir</a>: Acquired from <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Primeval Sorcerer Azur" href="/Primeval+Sorcerer+Azur" target="">Primeval Sorcerer Azur</a> sitting near the cliffs in the northeast. <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Interactive map?id=2307&amp;lat=-89.835938&amp;lng=70.905647&amp;zoom=8" href="/Interactive+map?id=2307&amp;lat=-89.835938&amp;lng=70.905647&amp;zoom=8">Elden Ring Interactive Map Link</a>.</p> </li> 
</ul> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring Comet Azur Notes &amp; Tips</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>This spell does not count as a charge spell, and therefore does not benefit from&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Godfrey Icon" href="/Godfrey+Icon">Godfrey Icon</a>.</li> 
 <li>Damage can be boosted by 15% by wearing <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Azur's Glintstone Crown" href="/Azur's+Glintstone+Crown">Azur's Glintstone Crown</a>. This comes at the cost of a 15% increase in ALL sorcery costs.</li> 
 <li>Can be cast&nbsp;continuously by using <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Cerulean Hidden Tear" href="/Cerulean+Hidden+Tear">Cerulean Hidden Tear</a>.</li> 
</ul> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Best Comet Azur Buffs</h3> 
<p>Use these&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Buffs and Debuffs" href="/Buffs+and+Debuffs">Buffs</a>&nbsp;to maximize the performance of the Comet Azur spell. Note that increases in attack power are multiplicative unless stated otherwise.</p> 
<div style="max-width: 600px;"> 
 <details> 
  <div class="table-responsive"> 
   <table class="wiki_table"> 
    <tbody> 
     <tr> 
      <td style="width: 151px; text-align: center;"> <p><strong>Comet Azur</strong></p> </td> 
