      <td style="width: 206.969px; text-align: center;">+15%&nbsp;Attack Power</td> 
      <td style="width: 535.031px; text-align: center;">All spells cost 15% more <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring FP" href="/FP">FP</a> to cast.</td> 
     </tr> 
     <tr> 
      <td style="width: 151px; text-align: center;"><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Cerulean Hidden Tear" href="/Cerulean+Hidden+Tear">Cerulean Hidden Tear</a></td> 
      <td style="width: 206.969px; text-align: center;">Spell Has No&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring FP" href="/FP">FP</a>&nbsp;Cost</td> 
      <td style="width: 535.031px; text-align: center;">Lasts 15 seconds. Allows for you to keep activating the spell for far longer than you normally&nbsp;can, dealing massive damage on stationary targets.</td> 
     </tr> 
     <tr> 
      <td style="width: 151px; text-align: center;"><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Graven-Mass Talisman" href="/Graven-Mass+Talisman">Graven-Mass Talisman</a></td> 
