     </tr> 
     <tr> 
      <td style="width: 151px; text-align: center;"><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Lord of Blood's Exultation" href="/Lord+of+Blood's+Exultation">Lord of Blood's Exultation</a></td> 
      <td style="width: 206.969px; text-align: center;">+20% Attack&nbsp;Power</td> 
      <td style="width: 535.031px; text-align: center;">Lasts 20 seconds when a nearby player or enemy is inflicted with blood loss. Can be self-inflicted with <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Seppuku" href="/Seppuku">Seppuku</a>. Stacks with Kindred of Rot's Exultation.</td> 
     </tr> 
     <tr> 
      <td style="width: 151px; text-align: center;"><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Kindred of Rot's Exultation" href="/Kindred+of+Rot's+Exultation">Kindred of Rot's Exultation</a></td> 
      <td style="width: 206.969px; text-align: center;">+20% Attack Power</td> 
      <td style="width: 535.031px; text-align: center;">Lasts 20 seconds when a nearby player or enemy is inflicted with poison or rot. Can be self-inflicted with <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Raw Meat Dumpling" href="/Raw+Meat+Dumpling">Raw Meat Dumpling</a>. Stacks with Lord of Blood's Exultation.</td> 
     </tr> 
     <tr> 
      <td style="width: 151px; text-align: center;"><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Magic Scorpion Charm" href="/Magic+Scorpion+Charm">Magic Scorpion Charm</a></td> 
