      <td style="width: 535.031px; text-align: center;">Lasts 30 seconds.</td> 
     </tr> 
     <tr> 
      <td style="width: 151px; text-align: center;"> <p><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Ritual Sword Talisman" href="/Ritual+Sword+Talisman">Ritual Sword Talisman</a></p> <p>or</p> <p><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Red-Feathered Branchsword" href="/Red-Feathered+Branchsword">Red-Feathered Branchsword</a></p> </td> 
      <td style="width: 206.969px; text-align: center;"> <p>+10%&nbsp;Attack Power</p> <p>or</p> <p>+20% Attack Power</p> </td> 
      <td style="width: 535.031px; text-align: center;"> <p>Must be at full health</p> <p>or</p> <p>Must be below 20%&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring HP" href="/HP">HP</a>.</p> </td> 
     </tr> 
     <tr> 
      <td style="width: 151px; text-align: center;"><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Terra Magica" href="/Terra+Magica">Terra Magica</a></td> 
