<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Comet Azur Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li><a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Primeval Sorceries" href="/Primeval+Sorceries">Primeval Sorcery</a></li> 
 <li>Stamina Cost:&nbsp;34</li> 
 <li>Deals magic damage</li> 
</ul> 
